// Shared icon entry wrapper. Maps generic icon variants to the prepared
// rawfile SVG assets (stroke-mode by default). Per the SVG gate, rawfile stroke
// icons are rendered with Image($rawfile(...)) and never chained with
// .fillColor() — active/inactive states switch the rawfile variant instead.
